org.ambraproject.rhino.view.journal

Class JournalNonAssocView

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ambraproject.rhino.view.journal.JournalNonAssocView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JsonOutputView

    public class JournalNonAssocView
extends Object
implements JsonOutputView
    A view of a Journal object that does not serialize its associative volumes field. Therefore, it is safe to serialize a Journal wrapped in this class regardless of whether/how its associative fields were initialized.

    Other than omitting that field, the view is homomorphic to the default serialization of a bare Journal object.
